# Android ExecuTorch Reference Bundle

Base model: `{{BASE_MODEL}}`

## Prerequisites
- Android Studio Hedgehog+ (or newer)
- Android SDK 34
- JDK 17
- Gradle 8+

## Model Placement
1. Copy model artifacts into `android/app/src/main/assets/models/`.
2. Recommended primary artifact name: `model.bin`.
3. Keep tokenizer/config files in the same `models/` directory when available.

## Run Instructions
1. Run: `bash scripts/run_android_app.sh`
2. Open the `android/` folder in Android Studio if you prefer IDE setup.
3. Launch the app on emulator/device and press Generate.

## Smoke Inference
Run: `bash scripts/run_smoke.sh "Hello from Android"`
